og.description: Sales at U.S. pharmacies and drug stores are looking healthier,  as growing demand for medications and the impact of the Affordable Care Act begin to take hold. New data from Sageworks, a financial information company, show that sales among privately held pharmacies and drug stores (NAICS 446110) rose 6.3 percent in [...]
